                                                                       Name range function
                                                                          
                                                             =AVERAGE(A2:A12)
                                                             =STDDEV(A2:A12)
                                                             
                                                             For appending the information,
                                                             =OFFSET($A$2,0,0,count($A,$A),1)
                                                             Syntax: (Starting point,row,column,height,weight)
                                                             
                                                             Put offset function in name manager.
                                                             
                                                             IF Statement
                                                             
                                                             =IF(B2 = 2, "Equals to 2","doesn't equal 2")
                                                             
                                                             AND Function
                                                             
                                                             =AND(FALSE,TRUE) -> FALSE
                                                             
                                                             OR Function
                                                             
                                                             =OR(FALSE,TRUE) -> TRUE
                                                             
                                                             COUNTIF AND SUMIF
                                                             
                                                             =COUNTIF($A$2:$A$12,H3)
                                                             
                                                             =SUMIF($A$2:$A$12,H3,F2:F12)
                                                             
                                                             UNIQUE Function can be used to get unique values,
                                                             SORT function can be used to sort them.
                                                             
                                                             SUMIFS for multiple if statements.
                                                             
                                                             <> not =
                                                             =AVERAGEIF(F2:F5,"<>9999")
                                                             
                                                              Flash fill:
                                                              Data -> Data tools -> Flash fill
                                                              Fills data accordingly
                                                              
